@startuml Secventa Rezolvare Exercitiu
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title Diagrama de secvență — Rezolvarea unui exercițiu

actor "Elev" as Student
participant "Frontend\n(React Native)" as FE
participant "Backend\n(FastAPI)" as BE
database "MongoDB" as DB
participant "MathTutor\n(Rule-Based)" as Solver
participant "DeepSeek-R1\n+ QLoRA\n(Kaggle/Flask)" as LLM

Student -> FE : Selectează Subiect (I/II/III)
FE -> BE : GET /api/exercises?subject=1
BE -> DB : find(subject: 1)
DB --> BE : exerciții JSON
BE --> FE : lista exerciții
FE --> Student : Afișează exercițiu

Student -> FE : Trimite răspuns
FE -> BE : POST /api/exercises/submit-answer
BE -> BE : _answers_match()\nnormalizare + comparare
BE -> DB : insert attempt
BE -> DB : update XP (+10)

alt Răspuns CORECT
    BE --> FE : {correct: true, xp: 10}
    FE --> Student : "Corect! +XP"\n(confetti animation)
else Răspuns GREȘIT
    BE --> FE : {correct: false}
    FE --> Student : "Încearcă din nou!"

    Student -> FE : Cere rezolvare
    FE -> BE : POST /api/solver/solve

    BE -> Solver : Detectare tip exercițiu\n(regex)

    alt MathTutor poate rezolva
        Solver --> BE : Soluție pas cu pas\n(100% corect)
    else MathTutor NU poate
        BE -> LLM : POST /ask (Flask+ngrok)
        LLM -> LLM : <think>\nRaționament pas cu pas\n</think>
        LLM --> BE : Soluție + pași
    end

    BE --> FE : {solution, steps}
    FE --> Student : Rezolvare pas cu pas
end

@enduml
